","tid":1887854,"uid":121196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T03:59:33.000Z","msg":"警黑勾結"},{"pid":"5b39110eed8b21ce685419bd637d2e44557e77d8","tid":1887854,"uid":100930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T04:13:04.000Z","msg":"好撚記得"},{"pid":"0c74027f44486d9140c8c23ad7fef1e12723859c","tid":1887854,"uid":217089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T08:35:38.000Z","msg":"熱門一個post都無"},{"pid":"26e0229caf8edfe50a8e684b014600313ebf63d9","tid":1887854,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:12:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d4305da8beff97ee7e6f29bdc68b130e306d1e3","tid":1887854,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T11:17:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39ae1734d53aef81704f83bde19825c72597499d","tid":1887854,"uid":69629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qvgctu9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqvgctu9.jpg&h=7227db22&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea9062608dbbfe9cafc4c16cd6481c15e00f81cd","tid":1887854,"uid":238340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:43:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dc0c8c722ebe9be2b187d07f5eb8be437b96b9ec","tid":1887854,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:44:33.000Z","msg":"認真睇哂佢plz <br />\n<br />\nTerry Yeung:<br />\n新聞跑來了。「文宣平台」複製貼上，再推農場內容謀利；兩登網友群起轉發，內容被一覽無遺。<br />\n<br />\n點擊沒了，連帶的商業價值都被抹殺。有些媒體，如《蘋果》，更是走會員制。<br />\n<br />\n試問，你忽然尊重的媒體工作者，要怎樣謀生？<br />\n<br />\n半年來，愈見惡化。議題被網民壞習慣，以及網軍的無形之手操控。<br />\n<br />\n然後你說：運動靜咗好多。<br />\n<br />\n改變自己，改變習慣。<br />\n<br />\n1. 不是正統媒體的新聞，不轉發。<br />\n2. 未經Fact Check、來自內容農場的消息，不要理。<br />\n3. 很多文宣大台都是盜取內容，不轉發。<br />\n4. 只轉發原創者的內容<br />\n5. 貼報道上討論區，只取少量內容，放link鼓勵點擊（尢其文宣大台該帶頭做）。<br />\n<br />\n再重覆，目標為上，才可以拯救連登垂死的熱門。<br />\n<br />\n比方說，<br />\n1. 如果兩日後有遊行，專注推行動Post；<br />\n2. 同一議題，集中處理，不要分散；<br />\n3. 有人留言「拉」，網友不需再留言；<br />\n4. 戒除政治J女性癖，不要再討論區議員身材；<br />\n5. 未能Fact Check的事情，忍痛讓佢沉。<br />\n6. 減少用極端字眼，例如「就嚟輸」；<br />\n7. 至為重要：不 要 再 推 假 標 題<br />\n<br />\n每個手足都有責任打好呢場資訊戰，改變習慣，重奪輿論主導權，大家一定做得到。<br />\n<br />\nYoutube戰線：黃色資訊片一律Coment+Like+Share&amp;Subscribe（CLS)（share做唔到的話重要片先share)<br />\n<br />\n香港人，改變。<br />\n<br />\nP.S.如果覺得有意思，煩請分享，謝謝你。<br />\n-------------------------------------------<br />\nIG：Terry_yeung_blog<br />\nIG連結：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IMS6HI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IMS6HI&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5EngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=83d23037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IMS6HI</a>"},{"pid":"bcc4bb69db87060b0822a5bb3da33149655af77c","tid":1887854,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39ae1734d53aef81704f83bde19825c72597499d","tid":1887854,"uid":69629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qvgctu9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqvgctu9.jpg&h=7227db22&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:45:41.000Z","msg":"推呢個"},{"pid":"1eb3e9da91a7a2dbe6fbd90d39a20a45a54102a2","tid":1887854,"uid":225885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:46:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0986b054cb5bca8c2a5506bbfe281671ddfd66ac","tid":1887854,"uid":2248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T20:17:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"aaa8540007bc74609543bc17f41a827b72650d49","tid":1887854,"uid":2248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T20:17:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a08a5e395b239d92088